nodes.bodyText:
I prefer to keep the code as is as it is more compact and I don't think readability is dramatically different between the two options:
current option:
return n == CANCELLED ? CANCELLED + 1 : n == 0 ? -1 : n;

suggested option:
if (n == CANCELLED) {
  return CANCELLED + 1;
}
return n == 0 ? -1 : n;

